Name: django-smart-settings
Version: 0.1.2
Summary: Helper for django settings
Home-page: https://github.com/ertwroc/django-smart-settings
Author: ERt
Author-email: ert.wroc@gmail.com
License: LICENSE.txt
Description: django-smart-settings
        =====================
        
        How to install
        
        pip install django-smart-settings
        
        How to use
        
        Create your Django project
        Create directory settings next to settings.py file
        Move settings.py to settings/ and rename it to default.py
        Create settings/__init__.py
        Add in this file:
        import django_smart_settings
        
        django_smart_settings.configure(locals())
Platform: UNKNOWN
